TextEng: I'm not here to apprentice for anything.
Text: 전 아무것도 도제가 되러 온 게 아니에요.

TextEng: Are you sure? I'd really like to sign up.

Text: 나 도제 되러 온 거 아니야.

TextEng: Is you sure? Me really wants to sign up.
Text: 너 확실해? 나 진짜 가입하고 싶어.

TextEng: What kind of guild is this?
I'd like to ask some questions.
You says this place is guild?
Pleased to meet you. My name is <FullName>.
You don't need to know who I am.
Me be pleased to meet you. Me name <FullName>.
You no needs know who me is.
Text: 너 나 누군지 알 필요 없어.

TextEng: If me gets coin enough, sure.
Do you sell arms and armor, then?
Can I hire one of your mercenaries?
Text: 용병 한 명 고용할 수 있나요?

TextEng: Let me ask you something else.
Can me hires a mercenary from you?
Text: 나 너한테서 용병 고용할 수 있어?

TextEng: Is there a good inn nearby?
Is there a decent store in town?
Is there a druid grove in the area?
How do I get to Luskan from here?
Can one get magical supplies in town?
Text: 마을에서 마법 물자를 구할 수 있나요?

TextEng: Me gets magic stuff around heres?
Text: 나 여기 주변에서 마법 물건 얻어?

TextEng: I have one of the ears.
What have you heard about the plague in Neverwinter?
Do you know of anything odd in the area?
Text: 이 지역에 뭔가 이상한 일 아나요?

TextEng: I'm looking for work, if you know of any.
Text: 일자리를 찾고 있는데, 아시면 말씀해 주세요.

TextEng: I have some questions about the bounties.
Text: 현상금에 대해 몇 가지 질문이 있어요.

TextEng: What you hear 'bout sickness in Neverwinter?
You know about strange stuff going on?
Me has questions about escaped guys.
Just how dangerous are these men?
So I would have to bring back their ear?
So me would brings the ear?
My mistake, I don't have anything.
Thank you, that would be fine.
I was glad to rid the world of the vermin. I need no reward.
Text: 세상에서 해충을 없애서 기뻤어요. 보상은 필요 없어요.

TextEng: Me happy to kills bad guy. Me need nothin' for it.
Text: 나 나쁜 놈 죽여서 기뻐. 나 그거로 아무것도 필요 없어.

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> Surely the town's safety is worth more than that.
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 분명히 마을의 안전은 그보다 더 가치 있을 텐데요.

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> Town safe, now. That's worth more golds, maybe?
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 마을 안전해, 이제. 그거 금 더 많이 가치 있어, 어쩌면?

TextEng: Add more gold to that, or loose convicts will be the least of your problems...
Text: 거기 금 더 추가해요, 안 그러면 탈옥수들이 당신 문제 중에 가장 작은 게 될 거예요...

TextEng: You adds more gold, or me be worse than bad guys!
Text: 너 금 더 추가해, 안 그러면 나 나쁜 놈들보다 더 나쁠 거야!

TextEng: Me no find them yet, no.
Text: 나 아직 그들 못 찾았어, 아니.

TextEng: What bounties are you talking about?
Uh... me know of no bounties.
Why don't you and your men get her back?
Text: 왜 당신과 부하들이 그녀를 되찾아오지 않나요?

TextEng: Do you know where she's being held?
And what might my reward be for doing that?
Text: 그걸 하면 제 보상이 뭐가 되나요?

TextEng: Why you and soldier guys not go gets her?
Text: 왜 너랑 병사 놈들이 그녀 데리러 안 가?

TextEng: What I gets if me saves her?
What about bounties? Me has ear.

Text: 무슨 일이 있었는지 다시 말해 주세요.

TextEng: I'm sorry, Kendrack... but Shaldrissa died. I tried my best.
Text: 미안해요, 켄드랙... 하지만 샬드리사가 죽었어요. 최선을 다했어요.

TextEng: No, she's dead. Them's the breaks.
I'll go look for her now.
Find her yourself. I have other problems.
Text: 직접 찾으세요. 저한테는 다른 문제가 있어요.

TextEng: You tells me what happen again.
Text: 무슨 일 있었는지 다시 말해 줘.

TextEng: Me sorry, Kendrack... but Shaldrissa dead. Me try hard.
Text: 나 미안해, 켄드랙... 하지만 샬드리사 죽었어. 나 열심히 했어.

TextEng: Nope, she dead. Is bad luck, me guesses.
Text: 아니, 그녀 죽었어. 나쁜 운이야, 나 생각해.

TextEng: Me go looks for her now.
You finds her. Me have big problems of me own.
Text: 너 그녀 찾아. 나 내 자신의 큰 문제 있어.
